file.name: oneOfRequest.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Example-Combined-OneOf
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: /webservice/REST/combined-OneOf
    variables: {}
paths:
  /pets:
    patch:
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              oneOf:
                - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Cat'
                - $ref: '#/components/schemas/Dog'
      responses:
        '200':
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                oneOf:
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/CatResponse'
                  - $ref: '#/components/schemas/DogResponse'

components:
  schemas:
    Dog:
      type: object
      properties:
        bark:
          type: boolean
        breed:
          type: string
          enum: [Dingo, Husky, Retriever, Shepherd]
    Cat:
      type: object
      properties:
        hunts:
          type: boolean
        age:
          type: integer
    CatResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        customField:
          type: string
    DogResponse:
      type: object
      properties:
        color:
          type: string

Error: notImplemented: path "/pets": patch: responses: 200: contents: unsupported content types: [text/plain]
